WEBVTT

00:06:01.748 --> 00:06:04.198
One of the first questions I asked was,

00:06:04.222 --> 00:06:07.865
"Where did this idea
of being a white person

00:06:07.889 --> 00:06:09.538
come from in the first place?"

00:06:10.592 --> 00:06:12.984
Science is clear.

00:06:13.008 --> 00:06:15.152
We are one human race.

00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:16.973
We're all related,

00:06:16.997 --> 00:06:19.843
all descended from
a common ancestor in Africa.

00:06:20.772 --> 00:06:24.517
Some people walked out of Africa
into colder, darker places

00:06:24.541 --> 00:06:27.093
and lost a lot of their melanin,

00:06:27.117 --> 00:06:28.862
some of us more than others.

00:06:28.886 --> 00:06:30.115
(Laughter)